{"tid":388062,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"981同522各位手足點睇","createTime":"2017-09-05T07:19:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T05:26:04.000Z","uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9f8158cb3b91ec46381e56e9c9722993d91b644c","tid":388062,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T07:19:22.000Z","msg":"心思思想8蚊入981搏上9蚊，10x入522搏上返11x<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知各位手足點睇？"},{"pid":"87b654cb75ad1e3f4e54d494339018fffa7fc90c","tid":388062,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T07:19:58.000Z","msg":"981搏上9蚊<br />\n笑到仆街"},{"pid":"db49c6df5d353fb10907cc5354859109387e3d1a","tid":388062,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T07:20:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>981搏上9蚊<br />\n笑到仆街</blockquote><br />\n新手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打有咩高見"},{"pid":"5bc04f0c3d8db9b4bbb65cadb53d36b9df2481bb","tid":388062,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T07:22:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>981搏上9蚊<br />\n笑到仆街</blockquote><br />\n利申非即日鮮，不過覺得間公司廢廢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不務正業r&amp;d又廢"},{"pid":"0269ae60aaa8ac87b93c0f5d5f224ae973b51d6b","tid":388062,"uid":22832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T07:24:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>981搏上9蚊<br />\n笑到仆街</blockquote><br />\n新手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打有咩高見</blockquote><br />\n981 d野冇競爭力<br />\n純粹係大陸開間公司整黎做半導體研究<br />\n但係根本唔夠人勁<br />\n<br />\n隻股個價間唔中係會抽升<br />\n不過最終黎講都係跌勢<br />\n唔好俾佢呃到<br />\n如果你有貨就好放啦<br />\n一個月後變做七蚊你唔好喊"},{"pid":"244ee39394c48716e3960e4664b760e11afb8b5d","tid":388062,"uid":67823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T07:25:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">981</span> 技術工藝水平不足，最薄只係做到28nm，睇番Q416 result, revenue 只有 3.5% 係黎自 28nm wafer. 而現時其他大 semiconductor manufacturer (TSM, Intel) 已經做 thickness 薄至 10 nm 既 wafer.  <br />\n<br />\nFY16 annual report 亦睇到981 gross profit 下趺, 反映競爭下毛利受壓, 而現時 semiconductor 既其中一個growth driver 來自手機. 手機廠商為加大電池容量但又不影響手機 thickness, 入面的 chip-set 需要變薄. Samsung s8 的手機 chipset 已經是 10nm 厚.<br />\n<br />\n所以鬥技術, 981真係唔夠鬥, 鬥平既話就大件事.<br />\n做chip-set 對硬件投資大, 帶來既風險同回報一樣高, 一追不上技術含量就等於倒錢落海, 呢方面內地係一定程度上係追唔上外國.</blockquote><br />\n純真猛男巴打四月中喺5%post嘅一個分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d623b6444c6754da8bb6628ba60692bbb0a20fb2","tid":388062,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T07:26:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>981搏上9蚊<br />\n笑到仆街</blockquote><br />\n新手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打有咩高見</blockquote><br />\n981 d野冇競爭力<br />\n純粹係大陸開間公司整黎做半導體研究<br />\n但係根本唔夠人勁<br />\n<br />\n隻股個價間唔中係會抽升<br />\n不過最終黎講都係跌勢<br />\n唔好俾佢呃到<br />\n如果你有貨就好放啦<br />\n一個月後變做七蚊你唔好喊</blockquote><br />\n多謝提點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁522呢間野巴打點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 前排一野震落黎個陣起98蚊入左少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0833018d06e8f6dad2c5e538d15eaae49d56a317","tid":388062,"uid":89066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T07:27:22.000Z","msg":"我都1